040_testing_200_0:
SELECT min(w_state) ,
       min(i_item_id) ,
       min(cs_item_sk) ,
       min(cs_order_number) ,
       min(cr_item_sk) ,
       min(cr_order_number)
FROM catalog_sales
LEFT OUTER JOIN catalog_returns ON (cs_order_number = cr_order_number
                                    AND cs_item_sk = cr_item_sk) ,warehouse ,
                                                                  item ,
                                                                  date_dim

  AND i_category = 'Children'
